  "title": "(6 months / Central) Videographer / Video Content Creator / Video Editor (Office Hours, 5 Days) #HMS",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>Create and develop marketing content for digital and print platforms to support outreach initiatives<br />Produce visual and promotional materials including basic photo and video content to enhance marketing efforts<br />Perform video recording, stitching, and editing using Adobe software to deliver polished video content<br />Update website content and coordinate marketing materials to maintain current and engaging information<br />Support event coordination and outreach activities to ensure smooth execution and participant engagement<br />Collate data, manage documentation, and coordinate administrative tasks to support marketing and training grant activities<br />Provide administrative and coordination support during the Training Grant evaluation phase to facilitate accurate assessments<br /><br />Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)<br />Company EA Licence number : 99C4599<br />Personnel EA License: R1331820</p>",
